pfsense

source.@value:
pipeline "pfs"
stage 0 match either
rule "write_utc_timestamp"
end

description.@value: write_utc_timestamp just in case your syslog provides non-utc unmarked timestamped
get_browser

source.@value:
rule "get_browser"
when
  has_field("http_user_agent")
then
let parsed = grok(pattern: "%{USER_BROWSER}",value: to_string($message.http_user_agent),only_named_captures: true);
set_fields(parsed);
end
